Enrique Murciano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Enrique_Murciano 0 Enrique Ricardo Murciano is an American actor. He is known for his role as FBI agent Danny Taylor in the CBS mystery drama series Without a Trace from 2002 to 2009. Enrique_Ricardo_Murciano is an_American_actor .
